The paper focuses on software engineering practices, specifically continuous integration, and its impact on software quality. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. The paper also involves programming languages (cs.PL), software development (cs.SD), machine learning (cs.LG), and cryptography (cs.CR) to some extent. However, these categories are less likely as they are not the primary focus of the paper.
